11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 2232, is
13 amended to read as follows:
14 Section 2232. The Commission, through the Oklahoma Tourism and
15 Recreation Department, may sponsor, promote, and implement an annual
16 statewide tourism and recreation industry conference to promote the
17 tourism and recreation industry. The Department is authorized to
18 may partner with private entities for the administration and
19 execution of the conference. The Department may enter into
20 contracts or agreements pursuant to this section on a fair and
21 reasonable basis in compliance with paragraph 10 of subsection C of
22 Section 85.5 of this title in an amount not to exceed Seventy-five
23 Thousand Dollars ($75,000.00). The Department is hereby authorized
24 to may charge registration and exhibit space fees necessary to cover
SENATE FLOOR VERSION - SB1525 SFLR Page 1
