1 the costs of the conference and shall deposit the fees plus any
2 other conference proceeds, including donated funds, into an agency
3 special account to be created by the Special Agency Account Board.
4 Expenditure of monies from the agency special account shall be for
5 purposes incidental to the tourism and recreation industry
6 conference, and shall be approved by the Commission Executive
7 Director.
8 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
9 COMMITTEE REPORT BY: COMMITTEE ON ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT, WORKFORCE
